mystic dragon.description: Mystic Dragon is a potent hybrid strain known for its deeply relaxing and euphoric effects. It’s characterized by a complex aroma and flavor profile, making it a popular choice for evening relaxation and creative pursuits.  The high THC content combined with moderate CBD offers a balanced experience.
mystic dragon.name: Mystic Dragon

nebula frost.description: Nebula Frost is a potent hybrid strain known for its frosty, resinous buds and deeply relaxing effects. It offers a balanced blend of cerebral and body high, making it a great choice for both recreational and medicinal users. The complex terpene profile contributes to its rich aroma and flavor.
nebula frost.name: Nebula Frost

zereal milk.description: Zereal Milk is a smooth and creamy hybrid strain known for its relaxing and grounding effects. It offers a balanced blend of euphoria and calm, making it a great choice for unwinding after a long day or managing discomfort. The terpene profile contributes to its soothing qualities, promoting relaxation and easing tension.
zereal milk.name: Zereal Milk
